item.title: First Time Nemophila REACT to " Rise" Official Live Version #nemophila #nemophilareaction #risereact
item.description: Welcome those of you catching my REACTION to Nemophila "Rise" and thanks to the Nemophila Fandom who have always treated me well in the comments section on these Bleeding Edge Reactions. I am still not super familiar with the band Nemophila, but this is my first-time reaction to "Rise" and it totally kicked my ass!!
